<ab facs="#facs_49_r2l4"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> volkmeır bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sıg<ex>mund</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r2l5">ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc künıg ʒu ſpeyr <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd nu herheim <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r2l6">dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns wol geſagt vvıe Jr Jn gar <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_49_r2l7"><expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyt . des wır ewch <expan>fleıſʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wır <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch </ab>
