<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Petre, als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd und
                <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Sebolt Pfinczing und
              <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeir bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund</ex></expan>, <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und zu
                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig, zu Speyr <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>
            und nu herheim <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
            wol gesagt, wie ir in gar <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und
                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt, des wir ewch <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wir <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, ob der
                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> der römisch künig, sein <expan>künikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>krönu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>empfahe<ex>n</ex></expan> wölt und wenn er das lant <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab und wahin, daz ir uns davon
                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, sovil ewch denn gefüklich sey. Das
                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch verdienen. Denn daz es
              <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>künikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seinen
                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gelükl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und wolgieng, das <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> uns ein
                <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> frewd und trost und <expan>horte<ex>n</ex></expan>
            das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> als pillich ist. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
